            <title><![CDATA[Split Fiction's Josef Fares Has "Already Started" Next Game, Clarifies Relationship With EA]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/split-fictions-josef-fares-has-already-started-next-game-clarifies-relationship-with-ea/1100-6530172/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
